578
00:43:44,410 --> 00:43:46,130
Was there . . .

579
00:43:46,690 --> 00:43:50,100
something recorded on there?

580
00:43:53,090 --> 00:43:54,880
By chance,

581
00:43:56,100 --> 00:43:58,180
is it related to my oldest brother?

