584
00:44:06,970 --> 00:44:10,770
I should have reported to the police right away at that time.

585
00:44:10,770 --> 00:44:15,040
It is all my fault because I was very scared.

586
00:44:16,070 --> 00:44:18,650
Where is it?

587
00:44:20,210 --> 00:44:22,420
The pen recorder?

