610
00:46:15,070 --> 00:46:17,450
 Then, your tongue will become paralyzed.

611
00:46:17,450 --> 00:46:20,190
 Eventually, you'll fall into a deep sleep.

612
00:46:23,550 --> 00:46:26,170
  What are you saying now?

