00:46:26,170 --> 00:46:29,290
 And you'll be discovered in the middle of a highway.

614
00:46:29,850 --> 00:46:32,520
 Death due to driving under the influence.

615
00:46:32,520 --> 00:46:34,660
  Jae Kyeong.

616
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:39,030
 I've been wishing for a long time 
for you to no longer be here.

617
00:46:41,230 --> 00:46:43,740
 You kept getting in the way.

618
00:46:44,860 --> 00:46:48,490
  With the reason that I was born later than you,

619
00:46:49,600 --> 00:46:52,680
 Father didn't give me any opportunities.

620
00:47:05,340 --> 00:47:07,680
 Please save me, Jae Kyeong!

621
00:47:51,830 --> 00:47:55,200
Why don't you open the trunk?

622
00:47:56,520 --> 00:47:58,480
Huh?

623
00:48:00,490 --> 00:48:02,690
Trunk?

624
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:07,530
Okay.

