Why make a person do it?

629
00:48:48,030 --> 00:48:49,930
Get in.

630
00:49:01,700 --> 00:49:04,300
 Isn't she Cheon Song Yi? 
 Is he her boyfriend?

631
00:49:05,500 --> 00:49:07,180
  Cheon Song Yi ♥ Do Min Joon

632
00:49:08,230 --> 00:49:09,880
What is this?

633
00:49:10,470 --> 00:49:12,260
Come here.

