00:49:32,850 --> 00:49:34,760
You're not supposed to undo it.

642
00:49:34,760 --> 00:49:39,360
Our destinies are locked up together here,
 so they can't be forever undone.

643
00:49:39,360 --> 00:49:43,290
An everlasting dependency, a complete bond. 
Something like that.

644
00:49:49,920 --> 00:49:51,280
Clickety-clack.

