648
00:50:01,510 --> 00:50:04,140
No. I like it.

649
00:50:04,620 --> 00:50:06,930
What is this? I am Cheon Song Yi.

650
00:50:06,930 --> 00:50:11,110
Do Min Joon, aren't you being too naive? You're a bit complacent.

