There is something I have to say.

682
00:52:36,620 --> 00:52:38,970
Ok, I understand.

683
00:52:39,500 --> 00:52:41,190
Cheon Song Yi.

684
00:52:41,190 --> 00:52:42,510
Huh?

685
00:52:43,810 --> 00:52:47,210
I'll be back soon. Wait for me.

